messages.messageBody:
**Is there another list just for conference/gathering announcements?**

http://groups.yahoo.com/group/unschoolingcircuitriders/

I'm trying to keep a map up of scheduled gatherings
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/unschoolingcircuitriders/app/placesmap/view/map

It's a really low traffic list, for folks who want to keep informed of
gatherings without having to find the information in among everything else.

Of course, folks holding gatherings will probably still want to post the
information as widely as possible, not just to Circuit Riders. :)

Deborah in IL
